# Image Processing API

## Description

A RESTful API built with **Express** and **TypeScript** that processes images using the **Sharp** library. It accepts image filenames and optional dimensions as query parameters, resizes the image accordingly, and returns the result. This project is part of the Udacity Full-Stack Web Developer Nanodegree program.

## Setup

Install dependencies:

```bash
npm install
```

Or to replicate from scratch:

```bash
npm init -y
npm i express sharp typescript
npm i -D @types/express @types/node @types/sharp @types/supertest nodemon \
    eslint @eslint/js typescript-eslint globals eslint-config-prettier \
    eslint-plugin-prettier prettier jasmine jasmine-spec-reporter supertest ts-node
```

## File Structure

```
Image Processing API/
